videos.headline: Hurts connects with Hall for a Sooners TD
videos.description: Jalen Hurts darts a pass to Jeremiah Hall who brings it in for a eight-yard Sooners touchdown to give them a 14-0 lead over the Coyotes.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Hurts connects with Hall for a Sooners TD) 2019/09/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Coyotes' Case makes diving TD catch
videos.description: Kody Case makes a diving catch for a 23-yard South Dakota touchdown to give the Coyotes their first score of the game.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Coyotes' Case makes diving TD catch ) 2019/09/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Stevenson breaks out for 75-yard Sooner TD run
videos.description: Oklahoma's Rhamondre Stevenson breaks free for a 75-yard touchdown run to give the Sooners a 56-7 lead over the Coyotes.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Stevenson breaks out for 75-yard Sooner TD run) 2019/09/07 ESHEET
